"- ISO: Week 1 starts on the Monday before the first Thursday of January.\n"
"- US: Week 1 starts on Jan 1. All other weeks start on Sunday.\n"
"- Instance: Week 1 starts on Jan 1. All other weeks start on the day defined in your Metabase localization settings."
msgstr "Neobvezno. Privzeto je `\"ISO\"`.\n"
"- ISO: teden 1 se začne v ponedeljek pred prvim četrtkom v januarju.\n"
"- US: teden 1 se začne 1. januarja. Vsi ostali tedni se začnejo v nedeljo.\n"
"- instanca: teden 1 se začne 1. januarja. Vsi ostali tedni se začnejo na dan, določen v tvojih Metabase nastavitvah lokalizacije."

#: frontend/src/metabase/querying/expressions/config.ts:1073
msgid "Takes a datetime and returns an integer (`1`-`31`) with the number of the day of the month."
msgstr "Vzame datum in čas ter vrne celo število (`1`-`31`) s številko dneva v mesecu."

#: frontend/src/metabase/querying/expressions/config.ts:1088
msgid "Takes a datetime and returns an integer (`1`-`7`) with the number of the day of the week. Which day is `1` is defined in your localization settings."
msgstr "Vzame datum in čas ter vrne celo število (`1`-`7`) s številko dneva v tednu. Kateri dan je `1`, je določeno v nastavitvah lokalizacije."

#: frontend/src/metabase/querying/expressions/config.ts:1102
msgid "Takes a datetime and returns an integer (`0`-`23`) with the number of the hour. No AM/PM."
msgstr "Vzame datum in čas ter vrne celo število (`0`-`23`) s številko ure. Brez AM/PM."

#: frontend/src/metabase/querying/expressions/config.ts:1116
msgid "Takes a datetime and returns an integer (`0`-`59`) with the number of the minute in the hour."
msgstr "Vzame datum in čas ter vrne celo število (`0`-`59`) s številko minute v uri."

#: frontend/src/metabase/querying/expressions/config.ts:1130
msgid "Takes a datetime and returns an integer (`0`-`59`) with the number of the seconds in the minute."
msgstr "Vzame datum in čas ter vrne celo število (`0`-`59`) s številko sekund v minuti."

